  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This was an unblinded randomized controlled trial. Women were randomized to uterine closure
      with the knotless barbed suture (Stratafix PDS, Ethicon) or Vicryl (Ethicon) at the time of
      elective cesarean. The primary outcome was closure time of the uterine incision. Also
      measured were blood loss during incision closure and the use of additional hemostatic
      sutures. Informed consent was obtained
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
